ress Stripe Payment Gateway allows your customers to enter their credit/debit card details during the purchase on the checkout page directly without leaving your site. It results in more successful payments and a better user experience. Accept Visa, Master...\";s:14:\"license_string\";s:29:\"rpress_stripe_payment_gateway\";s:10:\"class_name\";s:13:\"RPRESS_Stripe\";s:11:\"text_domain\";s:8:\"rpstripe\";}i:27;O:8:\"stdClass\":9:{s:2:\"id\";i:4297;s:5:\"title\";s:24:\"RazorPay Payment Gateway\";s:4:\"link\";s:56:\"https://restropress.com/addons/razorpay-payment-gateway/\";s:13:\"product_image\";s:61:\"https://restropress.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2021/11/14.png\";s:11:\"price_range\";s:2:\"46\";s:13:\"short_content\";s:279:\"Razorpay payment gateway plugin for RestroPress allows admin/store owners to accept credit cards, debit cards, net banking, wallet, UPI payments, etc. It allows customers to pay on your website with seamless integration, without being redirected away. This allows for refunds,...\";s:14:\"license_string\";s:31:\"rpress_razorpay_payment_gateway\";s:10:\"class_name\";s:15:\"rpress_RazorPay\";s:11:\"text_domain\";s:12:\"rpress_rzpay\";}}','no'),(255,'_transient_timeout_rpress_stats_earnings','1682624002','no'),(256,'_transient_rpress_stats_earnings','a:3:{s:32:\"aa923211a32ca9435f56abbb957ec78f\";i:0;s:32:\"7782d86a6845bb6e4ac281ea6664d274\";i:0;s:32:\"ea1438d55f26c03ec278b798a9ff4c6d\";i:0;}','no');
